{"tid":2125050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：是否全部死了？新城和香港電台都滅台了？如果是，這就好。可惜病毒太弱做不到。","createTime":"2020-07-26T01:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T08:55:19.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"adf53b948ecfb7b6b4c62c87c31701a6b4ba2385","tid":2125050,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"陳雲：金句對話。<br />\nA.A.： 佢最叻，自己索毒成功，累全台不特止&hellip;<br />\n//有新城內部人士指，程凱欣在疫情期間，無視疫情嚴重性，做節目時從來不喜歡戴口罩，拒戴的理由是太焗，而她更以節目質素為由，要求嘉賓和DJ在做節目時不可以戴口罩，最終自己中招。//<br />\n累埋街坊：<br />\n//鄧達智初步確診 曾到新城受訪，11日曾與資深歌手徐小鳳和黃淑儀等藝人見面，16日曾到港台主持節目，當日嘉賓劉天蘭要去做測試//<br />\n陳雲：是否全部死了？新城和香港電台都滅台了？如果是，這就好。可惜病毒太弱做不到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCFZYUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCFZYUK.png&h=1007658c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77cfed18bc4d586d20c04fc78740fb173b737152","tid":2125050,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dus5UtG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdus5UtG.jpg&h=bcd7db06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbPsom1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbPsom1.jpg&h=2d50eb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZLnWG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZLnWG2.jpg&h=4c54fa4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1X1ZetH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1X1ZetH.jpg&h=458a8e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4817d240d58ffbd8d11adcc2f6e588835349f484","tid":2125050,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n就差你呢個老癲佬未落埋去"},{"pid":"72c89062f59e318040286735e1e017c460ea3d5d","tid":2125050,"uid":66274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:17:49.000Z","ms